<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>وَهَذَا لَفْظُ عَبَّادِ بْنِ زِيَادٍ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَفِي الْبَابِ عَنْ عَائِشَةَ وَأَبِي سَعِيدٍ وَأَبِي هُرَيْرَةَ وَسَهْلِ بْنِ سَعْدٍ وَأَنَسِ بْنِ مَالِكٍ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَلا نَعْلَمُ فِي الْبَابِ حَدِيثًا لَهُ إِسْنَادٌ جَيِّدٌ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>